#. Tag: sect2
#: contexthelp.docbook:1
#, no-c-format
msgid "&WORK-IN-PROGRESS;"
msgstr "&WORK-IN-PROGRESS;"

#. Tag: para
#: contexthelp.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many functions and views have help and hints that can be displayed with the "
"<emphasis>What's This</emphasis> function."
msgstr ""
"Veel functies en weergaven hebben hulp en tips die getoond kunnen worden met "
"de functie <emphasis>Wat is dit</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: contexthelp.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can activate it with the menu entry <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>WhatsThis</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or keyboard "
"shortcut <keycombo>&Shift;<keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"U kunt het activeren met het menu-item <menuchoice><guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>WatIsDit</guimenuitem></menuchoice> of sneltoets "
"<keycombo>&Shift;<keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: contexthelp.docbook:7
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In dialogs it is activated by pressing the <varname>?</varname> in the "
"dialogs title bar."
msgstr ""
"In dialogen is het geactiveerd door op het <varname>?</varname> in de "
"dialogentitelbalk te klikken."
